Unilever May Buy OTP’s 10.6% Podravka Stake, Business.hr Says

-- B y   J a s m i n a   K u z m a n o v i c
-- 
2011-06-21T11:06:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-21/unilever-may-buy-otp-s-10-6-podravka-stake-business-hr-says.html
Unilever is interested in buying a
10.6 percent stake in Podravka Prehrambena Industrija d.d., held
by  Hungary ’s OTP Bank Nyrt.,  Business.hr  reported today without
saying where it got the information.  To contact the reporter responsible for the story:
Jasmina Kuzmanovic in Zagreb at 
 jkuzmanovic@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for the story:
James M. Gomez at   jagomez@bloomberg.net  